item.title: VIDEO ⟩ Elon Musk SHOCKS the World by Selling Twitter for Just 1 DOGE! Is This Real or a Prank?
item.description: In a jaw-dropping turn of events, tech maverick Elon Musk has sent the Twitterverse into a frenzy by allegedly selling the social media giant Twitter for a mere 1 DOGE, the cryptocurrency that started as a joke. Is this a wild stunt from the eccentric billionaire, or is there more to the story? Get ready for a rollercoaster ride of speculation and disbelief as the internet tries to make sense of Musk's latest move! 🚀🐕
item.author: Apollo.lv
